## naming convention

### case 1: value name is with two words: 
first character of first word is lower-case
first character of second word is upper-case
[e.g.] userName: this value consists of user + name. the value name should be userName

### case 2: API url is two words: 
first word and second word should be consisted of '_' 
[e.g.] /user/add_name
normally use '_' but other case might use '-'

